	   <tr><td colspan=2>Some FYIs here:<br><br>Top SKs use primarily 1h weapons... paladins use either but I believe their best weapons are 2h. Clerics almost always use 1h, epic or no, so a shield is a full-time piece of gear.<br><br>If you don't understand the value of AC to a cleric you've never played the high end game... WIS maxxes easily, AC is something you'll always want more. The only things a high end cleric looks for are HP/AC/mana/STA, there's so much WIS on high end cleric gear that clerics doing VP could probably not go below 200 WIS if they tried.<br><br>IF this was shaman usable THEN it would be ideal for them as well... I know I'd like a piece of gear like this so our guild shaman could survive slow/malo aggro better... however it's not so it's a moot point.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
